Question: āmittō, āmittere, āmīsī, āmissum
Answer: to send away; lose, let go
Name: āmittō, āmittere, āmīsī, āmissum

Question: alō, alere, aluī, altum
Answer: to nourish, support, sustain, increase; cherish
Name: alō, alere, aluī, altum

Question: stō, stāre, stetī, statum
